      ],
      "content": "A modest square of packed earth ringed by low stone buildings with slate roofs. A dry fountain stands in the centre, its basin cracked and filled with windblown leaves.\n\nClumps of **wild herbs** grow stubbornly from cracks in the stone around the fountain.\n\nSmoke drifts from a chimney to the east where a tavern sign swings on rusted chains. To the west, a gap between the houses opens onto dunes and the sound of surf."
    },
