      "content": "The low-ceilinged room is warm and dim, lit by tallow candles guttering in glass jars. A long bar of driftwood planks runs along the far wall, its surface stained dark with years of spilled ale.\n\nA **flour sack** leans against the bar, half-open.\n\nThe only way out is west, back to the square."
    },
